.Sh BUGS
Filenames aren't aligned vertically in list output.
.Pp
An option to modify the string separating filenames from timestamps is needed.
Something as simple as an
.Fl 0
switch for NUL-delimited output might suffice.
.
.Pp
Options for displaying inode change timestamps and birthtimes should be added.
Setting these fields to an arbitrary date appears to be impossible,
so an
.Fl b
and
.Fl c
option should be supported only when printing stats,
and issue an error if attempted to be used when setting utimes.
.
.Pp
Non-existent files are created when setting timestamps,
which is an undesired parallel with
.Xr touch 1
that goes against this program's intended purpose \
of only operating upon
.Em existing
files.
Users can always use
.Xr touch 1
followed by
.Nm
if they need to create
.Em and
set the timestamp of a hitherto non-existent file.
.
.Pp
Examples of
.Fl m
and
.Fl a
switch usage,
in both getter and setter operations,
should be added to this man page's
.Sx EXAMPLES
section.
